  {
    "key": "4af54e995c104423a796b64f651f63c56af699ae164f1906a02e93c2db9d3f7d",
    "original": "[img]gfx/ui/events/event_06.png[/img]%cripple% the cripple asks how %veteran% does it. The veteran raises an eyebrow.%SPEECH_ON%Do what?%SPEECH_OFF%The cripple bounces his head around as he figuratively beats around the bush.%SPEECH_ON%You know, it. Fight. Every time I get out there, I just think I'm not up to it, as though I were dragging you fellas down.%SPEECH_OFF%%veteran% laughs.%SPEECH_ON%Aye, I get what you mean. A cripple ain't fit for sellswording. But is that who you are? Just a cripple? Or are ye a man? You can choose to let your wobbles and ungainliness define who you are, or you can make your own path, as crooked and hobbled it may be.%SPEECH_OFF%Nodding, %cripple%'s face starts to glow.%SPEECH_ON%You're right. I'm not all that I could be and I got the body of a dying nun, but no man will put in more effort than I!%SPEECH_OFF%",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "Text = \"[img]gfx/ui/events/event_06.png[/img]%cripple% the cripple asks how %veteran% does it. The veteran raises an eyebrow.%SPEECH_ON%Do what?%SPEECH_OFF%The cripple bounces his head around as he figuratively beats around the bush.%SPEECH_ON%You know, it. Fight. Every time I get out there, I just think I'm not up to it, as though I were dragging you fellas down.%SPEECH_OFF%%veteran% laughs.%SPEECH_ON%Aye, I get what you mean. A cripple ain't fit for sellswording. But is that who you are? Just a cripple? Or are ye a man? You can choose to let your wobbles and ungainliness define who you are, or you can make your own path, as crooked and hobbled it may be.%SPEECH_OFF%Nodding, %cripple%'s face starts to glow.%SPEECH_ON%You're right. I'm not all that I could be and I got the body of a dying nun, but no man will put in more effort than I!%SPEECH_OFF%\""
  }
]